{{Infobox dungeon |name = Lostlorn Forest |image = [[File:Lostlorn Forest.png|300px]] |caption = A map of Lostlorn Forest. |tokens = 176,500 |location = Unova Route 16 }} '''Lostlorn Forest''' is a [[Dungeons|dungeon]] in [[Unova]]. It initially has 81 tiles arranged in an 9x9 square, including 9 chest tiles, 21 non-boss encounter tiles, and 1 boss encounter tile.
